      "writtenOn": "2026-07-14T12:47:53Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "This eventHandler is a PropertiesChanged signal match callback (registered via setupPropertiesChangedMatches, line 412, whose match rule is type\u003d\u0027signal\u0027). is_method_error() is only true for a method-call error reply — a signal is never a method error, so this condition is always false and the early return never fires, making the guard a no-op here. Did you observe an actual error message reaching this handler? Thanks.",
